Contellation COMBOS has a final assets done for new attack and has a flow graph of how the attack will work.

Description of attack:

Once an attack oppurtunity starts, the combo will start.

1. Both players have to fill out stars from The Big Dipper constellation
2. To fill out a star, you players must correctly input an array of inputs
3. An array of inputs is built off of P1's controls (WASD) and P2's controls (U,D,L,R) randomly
4. If the players succesfully press each input in the alloted time they add a star
5. If they misinput, then the attack finishes and will do damage proportional to the amount of stars succesfully added
6. If they complete the constellation, then the attack finished and do damage porportional to the amount of stars succesfully added (one shot)

